org.hypergraphdb.query

Class AnalyzedQuery<SearchResult>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hypergraphdb.HGQuery<SearchResult>
      • org.hypergraphdb.query.AnalyzedQuery<SearchResult>
  • Type Parameters:
    SearchResult -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    HGGraphHolder

    public class AnalyzedQuery<SearchResult>
extends HGQuery<SearchResult>

    A query object that holds information collected during the compilation process. When a HGQueryCondition is transformed into a HGQuery, it goes through several phases where the original condition and sub-conditions get transformed into other condition objects, as intermediary steps, and eventually into an executable HGQuery.
